    "body": "Thanks for the informative summary (with pictures). I think the current behavior comes from us drawing from the origin outward. This makes sense when going left to right, not so much bottom to top.\n\nI'd rather we have another keyword argument for this, since it will be an API change, something like `bar_order` or `group_order`.\n\nIt will be a bit before I can review the code.\n"
